STATE EX REL. DEBRUYNE
v.
LUCAS CTY. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS, JUVENILE DIV. 2018-0941 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 23, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and Fischer, DeWine, and Stewart, JJ., concur. Kennedy, French, and Donnelly, JJ., dissent.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Prohibition. On consideration of the merits, there is an adequate remedy at law. Writ denied.
